lead_paragraph: Manchester City continued their imperious start to the season with a 2-1 win over Swansea City to reach the fourth round of the League Cup on Wednesday but it was a testing night for rivals United who eventually overcame Northampton Town 3-1.

headline.print_headline: Manchester Rivals Win to Tee Up Fourth Round Tie
